data.meta_description:
31 likes, 2 comments - dannysinoffmusic on May 23, 2024: "Swinging with the great @jerryweldonmusic! Here is a clip of George and Ira Gershwin’s “They Can’t Take That Away From Me” with @ulyssesowensjr_ and @thomasmilovac from our concert @tribbyartscenter on May 7th. 

Looking forward to returning to Tribby on June 6th, when I’ll be singing with the Stardust Memories Big Band! I hope to see you there!
